div.div: The fourth season of Bungou Stray Dogs. No longer concerned with military affairs, Yukichi Fukuzawa intends to act as a lone bodyguard-for-hire, making use of his deadly swordsmanship. However, things are not going as planned for his freelance business, and that is when he crosses paths with a mouthy boy named Ranpo Edogawa. While their initial interactions are intertwined with a bizarre murder mystery, the aftermath prompts the formation of the Armed Detective Agency. Presently, Ranpo finds himself chasing down a gifted individual with the dangerous ability to execute the perfect crime. But as the great detective unravels the case, he soon discovers an elaborate plot to obliterate the Agency in its entirety. Although forewarned of the trap, the Agency continue their pursuit of the criminals, only to end up framed for the crime themselves. Now branded as wanted terrorists, the remaining members must find a way to prove their innocenceeven if they must turn to sworn enemies for assistance. (Source: MAL Rewrite)

Kirishima Tooru was accustomed to solving all problems through violence and was called the Demon of Sakuragi. One day, the boss of the Sakuragi family suddenly summons Kirishima and appoints him caretaker of his only daughter, Yaeka! A heartwarming comedy about a yakuza crime familys right-hand man and the boss only daughter. The two of them are about to begin their new daily lives together!
(Source: Crunchyroll, edited)
Koryuu nara Sude de Taosemasu kedo, Kore tte Joushiki janain desu ka?

Fil was raised in the mountains as the grandchild of humanitys strongest sage, inheriting his talent for magic, and strong enough to defeat dragons with her bare hands.
However, one day, the great sage summoned Fil to tell him:
Fil, youre actually a girl.
"Really!? By the way, whats a girl?"
Fil's ignorance of gender and other common sense knowledge worried the great sage. Concerned about her future, he decided to enroll Fil into the Royal Academy. It will be the start of an exciting school life for the innocent strongest girl!
(Source: Piccoma, translated)

Shizuku Hayama is the personal bodyguard for Ichika Kiryuin, the only daughter of a major industrialist. But Ichika is no shrinking violet, and she's perfectly able to handle any dangerous situation or challenge by herself. If Ichika doesn't need anyone protect her body, maybe Shizuku can help to protect her heart?
